    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my absolute dream of a car, and honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied this beauty from day one\u2014there's not a single scratch to be found and the interior is just spotless. It\u2019s been garage-kept and meticulously maintained, so it's running perfectly. If you\u2019re looking for something in truly pristine, like-new condition, this is definitely the one for you! Feel free to reach out if you want to take a look!",
