    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the marque\u2019s engineering prowess, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine with its signature individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing. The powertrain is mated to a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox, delivering linear power to a factory limited-slip differential. This chassis has undergone a proactive subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul to ensure long-term structural and mechanical integrity. The suspension maintains factory-spec geometry with refreshed bushings, preserving the sharp turn-in and communicative feedback inherent to the M-chassis. Meticulously serviced with a complete log of valve adjustments and fluid analyses, this vehicle represents a turn-key acquisition for the serious collector.",
      "price": 44500.0,
