    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offered here is a truly exceptional, collector-grade 2017 Porsche 718 Cayman in Graphite Blue Metallic. This vehicle is in absolute showroom condition, having been meticulously kept in a climate-controlled garage and driven only on fair-weather weekends. The exterior paint is flawless, protected by a professional ceramic coating that provides a deep, mirror-like finish with zero rock chips or swirl marks. Inside, the black leather interior still retains that 'new car' scent; there is no bolster wear, no scratches on the trim, and the carpets have been protected by premium mats since day one. Mechanically, the car is indistinguishable from new, with a full service history exclusively through Porsche dealerships. Every button, switch, and feature functions perfectly. It comes with two keys, all original manuals, and a clean title in hand. This is a rare opportunity to own a modern classic that has been preserved with obsessive attention to detail. Inspections are welcomed and encouraged.",
      "price": 46500.0,
